hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 定义与相似性变换
   $$u=U\,f'(\eta),\quad \eta=y\sqrt{\frac{U}{\nu x}},\quad dy=\sqrt{\frac{\nu x}{U}}\,d\eta.$$  
2. 动量厚度与能量厚度
   $$\theta=\int_0^\infty \frac{u}{U}\Bigl(1-\frac{u}{U}\Bigr)\,dy
   =\sqrt{\frac{\nu x}{U}}\int_0^\infty f'(\eta)\bigl(1-f'(\eta)\bigr)d\eta,$$  
   $$\delta_E=\int_0^\infty \frac{u}{U}\Bigl(1-\bigl(\tfrac{u}{U}\bigr)^2\Bigr)\,dy
   =\sqrt{\frac{\nu x}{U}}\int_0^\infty f'(\eta)\bigl(1-f'(\eta)^2\bigr)d\eta.$$
3. 壁面切应力与耗散
   $$\tau_w=\mu\Bigl(\frac{\partial u}{\partial y}\Bigr)_{y=0}
   =\mu\,U\sqrt{\frac{U}{\nu x}}\,f''(0)
   =\rho\nu U\sqrt{\frac{U}{\nu x}}\,\alpha,$$  
   $$D=\int_0^\infty\mu\Bigl(\frac{\partial u}{\partial y}\Bigr)^2dy
   =\rho\nu U^3\frac{1}{\sqrt{U\nu x}}\int_0^\infty(f'')^2d\eta
   =\rho\nu U^3\frac{I_D}{\sqrt{U\nu x}}.$$
4. 积分方程
   von Kármán 方程： 
   $$\frac{\tau_w}{\rho U^2}=\frac{d\theta}{dx}
   \;\Longrightarrow\;
   \frac{\alpha\nu}{\sqrt{U\nu x}}
   =\frac{d\theta}{dx}
   \;\Rightarrow\;
   \theta=2\alpha\sqrt{\frac{\nu x}{U}}.$$  
   能量方程： 
   $$\frac{2D}{\rho U^3}=\frac{d\delta_E}{dx}
   \;\Longrightarrow\;
   \frac{2\nu I_D}{\sqrt{U\nu x}}
   =\frac{d\delta_E}{dx}
   \;\Rightarrow\;
   \delta_E=4I_D\sqrt{\frac{\nu x}{U}}.$$
5. 形状因子
   $$H_E=\frac{\delta_E}{\theta}
   =\frac{4I_D\sqrt{\frac{\nu x}{U}}}{2\alpha\sqrt{\frac{\nu x}{U}}}
   =\frac{2I_D}{\alpha}.$$
